FUN FACTS ABOUT FOOD
(In the Planes) </p>

No one has to eat in the Astral Plane. Time is an illusion there, and no one gets hungry.
Arborea is the called 'the breadbasket of the planes.'
Tanar'ri feed on fear.
Undead are sustained, at least in part, by negative+energy.
Asuras subsist on positive+energy.
Slaadi like to eat mist mephits. Except when they don't.
All the vacuum mephits were eaten by vacuum quasielementals.
Sigil has to import all of its food.
A good way to prevent a Manes from regenerating is to eat it.</p>